 (Highest score is best)"}, "url": "http://gamerlimit.com/2011/04/gamer-limit-review-portal-2/"}, {"citation": "Problemen i Portal 2 f\u00e5r mig att k\u00e4nna mig precis lagom smart. Jag kommer p\u00e5 varje l\u00f6sning innan jag blir alltf\u00f6r irriterad. Valve har ocks\u00e5 byggt in pusslandet i en synnerligen v\u00e4lproducerad yta som ger det merv\u00e4rde som beh\u00f6vs f\u00f6r att jag inte ska tr\u00f6ttna p\u00e5 uppl\u00e4gget. F\u00f6r jag kan inte sticka under stol med att Portal 2 k\u00e4nns lite utdraget, trots enbart 5-6 timmars kampanj. Jag rekommenderar att ni spelar det i sm\u00e5 doser och i lugn och ro.", "date": "2011-04-19", "edit_object_url": "/approval/edit-object?type=47\u0026oid=45667648", "grade": null, "id": 218813, "internal_url": "https://www.mobygames.com/game/51233/portal-2/reviews/#critic-score-218813", "language": "sv", "max_score": 10.0, "normalized_score": 80.0, "platform": {"id": 81, "name": "PlayStation 3"}, "score": 8.0, "source": {"country": {"country_code": "se", "flag": "https://cdn.mobygames.com/9f3d1a06-ab5e-11ed-b6d6-02420a000150.gif", "id": 21, "name": "Sweden"}, "description": null, "edit_object_url": "/approval/edit-object?type=46\u0026oid=49257943", "first_year": 2001, "id": 1343, "internal_url": "https://www.mobygames.com/critic/1343/level-7/", "languages": [{"code": "sv", "id": 137, "name": "Swedish", "ordering": 1370}], "last_year": null, "name": "Level 7", "num_reviews": 176, "url": "http://level7.nu/"}, "submitter": {"id": 163111, "internal_url": "https://www.mobygames.com/user/163111/cavalary/", "name": "Cavalary"}, "type": {"id": 1, "name": "Numeric (Highest score is best)"}, "url": "http://level7.nu/spel/spel.php?id=5558\u0026show=text\u0026part=review\u0026aid=204061"}, {"citation": "Don\u0027t miss the chance to explore this meticulously designed digital playground.", "date": "2011-05-06", "edit_object_url": "/approval/edit-object?type=47\u0026oid=4295819381", "grade": null, "id": 510426, "internal_url